{
  "stem": "15721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because, of course, the anti-Semites made fun of the Eastern European Jews or Yiddish, and their behavior, they're-- they were, many of them were bearded, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father married this Eastern European Jewess on the day that he was called to the, to the army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave-- he was in uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gave him two hours I understand, of course, I wasn't there-- understand my mother fainted under the chuppah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she didn't see my father for quite a while after, till he had a furlough, during which they produced me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I was born in the middle of the war, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I can tell you, for instance, that my father's German family, during the four and 1/2 years that he was on the front, never wrote him, never sent him a package, because they were so outraged that he had tainted the family's reputation by marrying someone who was not a German Jewess.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother had the satisfaction that she was the only one in this rather large family that had three sons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all the bar mitzvahs happened in Munich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And over the years, she was and irresistibly charming lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she managed to convince the rest of my father's Germanic family that she was a worthy member.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, as I say, she helped produce those sons that became the, the next generation, at least in that regard.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So mother was an accomplished person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And despite the fact that she was of Eastern European descent, she became the president of the Women's Division of B'nai B'rith in Munich.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you must understand that B'nai B'rith in Europe altogether, but surely be in Germany, was the top Jewish organization with the greatest prestige.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
